  "description": "Free boundary condition lets the string ends vibrate — a glass harmonica quality, almost vocal in its resonance. Moderate stiffness, very low damping. Continuous bowing via sustain force, slow physics envelope for gradual harmonic build. LFO1 adds subtle vibrato. Poly4 for layered overtones.",
